{
  "stem": "26983.9",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could see from far, because what's happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a couple of hours, the SS man came, and I saw the table with all kinds of instruments for torture, which wasn't so pleasant.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't-- I didn't-- I wasn't beaten.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't tortured.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or punished at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He only asked me a few questions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said what I had to say before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I found it, and I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he left me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when I came back to our camp--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he let me go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Suddenly, more or less half of our boys were missing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a tremendous selection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, it shows you the irrational thing of Auschwitz, because this horrible, frightened scene saved me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because if I would be there--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More or less half were left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ja.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came to some other camps, and somewhere--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess about 40.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that is only one illustration how you should never--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember some of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Moishe ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dominic. ?] He had here his brother, and--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, at that time we didn't cry at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lost the crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were only thankful that-- what-- that we survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember also, on Yom Kippur, some people didn't eat and kept the soup-- which was very dangerous, because it's very hot and you should always keep your little thing where you kept your soup clean, and so on.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we put the soup under our bed and hoped it will be all right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a bit sour in the evening, but somehow we succeeded.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we saw in another block people parade-- few of the Jews parade on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
